### Recuperar todas las reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews

### Recuperar una review por id
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/41

### Recuperar todas las reviews de una pelicula
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/movie/1

### Recuperar todas las reviews de un usuario
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/user/1

### Crear una review
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "movieId": 1,
    "userId": 1,
    "rating": 4.0,
    "comment": "Great movie!"
}

### Actualizar una review
PATCH http://localhost:3000/reviews/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rating": 3.5
}

### Eliminar una review
DELETE http://localhost:3000/reviews/1